    <div class="construction-banner">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 1L21.5 6.5V17.5L12 23L2.5 17.5V6.5L12 1ZM12 3.31562L4.5 7.65334V16.3467L12 20.6844L19.5 16.3467V7.65334L12 3.31562ZM12 16C14.2091 16 16 14.2091 16 12C16 9.79086 14.2091 8 12 8C9.79086 8 8 9.79086 8 12C8 14.2091 9.79086 16 12 16ZM12 14C13.1046 14 14 13.1046 14 12C14 10.8954 13.1046 10 12 10C10.8954 10 10 10.8954 10 12C10 13.1046 10.8954 14 12 14Z"></path></svg>
      <div class="text-content">
        <h3 id="t-construction-title">持续构建中...</h3>
        <p id="t-construction-desc">更多增强功能与数据接口即将上线，敬请期待。</p>
